             320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 03:05:05 | 425 Mb
 

Trance Classics is aimed at providing a one-stop home for releases from some of the most well known names in the Trance Community. Rediscover some of your favorite tracks and explore their back catalogue even further as we serve them up in one great big accessible package! Why not kick things off with a bang... Solid Globe are the masterminds behind massive releases including North Pole, Sahara and Lost Cities. With special 2014 Remastered versions included, this is definitely a classics pack worth checking out.
